field.value:
I believe the MicroKernel framework should allow me to exclude one property of the dependency graph. 

This would allow this scenario (today  I get a circular reference type of stack overflow):

public class Parent{
  public Parent(Child child){
    this.child = child;
  }
  private Child child;
}

public class Child {
  public Child(){

  }
  private Parent parent;
  public Parent Parent{
    get{
      return parent;
    }
    set{
      parent = value;
    }
  }
}

Thanks a lot.
